    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus in a sophisticated Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been driven responsibly and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint maintains a high-quality finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor road-wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch. The interior is smoke-free and features Atlas Beige leather upholstery that remains supple and free of any rips or significant staining. All electronic features, including the dual-screen MMI touch response system, virtual cockpit, and Bang & Olufsen 3D Premium sound system, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; the 335-hp turbocharged V6 delivers power smoothly, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all weather conditions. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, new engine air filters, and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. The tires are matching Continentals with plenty of tread remaining. Included are two key fobs and a complete set of all-weather floor mats.",
